  <h2>Partnership Opportunities</h2>

  <h3>Featured Dealer Listings</h3>
  <p>Dealerships in high-traffic regions (TX, VA, MD, and the key content clusters) can be featured on model pages and in the "Best Chevy Dealer Near You" guide. Ideal for dealerships who want to reach in-market buyers doing their research before walking into a showroom.</p>

  <h3>Featured Mechanic & Shop Listings</h3>
  <p>Specialty shops (classic restoration, LS swaps, performance tuning, diesel, transmission) can be featured in our mechanic directory. Ideal for shops who do the real work, not just oil changes.</p>

  <h3>Sponsored Content</h3>
  <p>We occasionally publish sponsored content — full-length articles clearly labeled as "Partner Content" or "Sponsored." We will never publish sponsored content that doesn't match our editorial standards. If it's not worth reading, we won't write it.</p>

  <h3>Newsletter Sponsorship</h3>
  <p>Our newsletter reaches engaged Chevy enthusiasts weekly. One sponsor per issue, clearly labeled, with a short pitch and a click-through link.</p>

  <h3>Event & Travel Partnerships</h3>
  <p>State tourism boards and event organizers — we attend car shows regularly and can cover your event with Crystal on-site, photos, video, and a dedicated event report.</p>

  <h3>OEM & Press Loan Programs</h3>
  <p>We're interested in GM press fleet opportunities, Chevrolet Performance test vehicles, and OEM creator programs. Our coverage is honest — if the vehicle is great, we'll say so; if it isn't, we'll say that too.</p>

  <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
  <p>Email <a href="mailto:hello@chevyroots.com">hello@chevyroots.com</a> with "Partnership Inquiry" in the subject line. Tell us who you are, what you're selling, and who you'd like to reach. We respond within a few business days.</p>
